prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style raccoon wearing a tiny, slightly askew party hat, cheekily peeking over a giant, beautifully decorated birthday cake that takes up most of the scene. The raccoon has one paw dipped into the frosting, leaving a small smudge on its nose, and a mischievous glint in its big, innocent eyes. The cake is adorned with colorful sprinkles and a single, unlit candle. In the center of the image, overlaid on the cake, the word "birthday" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is rendered in a soft, lighthearted watercolor style, featuring artistic brush strokes, delicate color washes of pastel blues, pinks, and yellows, and visible paper texture with subtle, organic paint bleeds at the edges. Flat 2D artwork.
